attributes.Long form description: The student is disassembling a nightstand. The student removes all the screws and legs from the nightstand, and places them on the table.

attributes.Transcription: Okay now please disassemble the furniture.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the hex socket head of the nightstand.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student accidentally drops the allen wrench.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the first leg of the shelf and the top of the table.
The student unscrews the hex socket head of the nightstand.
The student disassembles the second leg of the shelf.
The student disassembles the third leg of the shelf and the top table.
The student disassembles the tray of the table.
The student disassembles the fourth leg of the table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student accidentally drop the allen wrench on the table.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the tray of the table.

attributes.Transcription: Okay now you can press the stop button.
